---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Gallery" description="Billiard, Tennis & Snowboarding Adventures">
  <div class="gallery-page">
    <h1>$ ls -la ~/adventures/</h1>
    <p>Beyond coding and trading systems, I enjoy staying active through various sports and recreational activities.</p>
    
    <div class="gallery-grid">
      <!-- Billiards Section -->
      <div class="gallery-section">
        <h2>üé± Billiards</h2>
        <div class="activity-card">
          <div class="placeholder-image billiards">
            <span>üé±</span>
            <p>Billiards Action Shot</p>
          </div>
          <div class="activity-content">
            <h3>Precision and Strategy</h3>
            <p>
              Like programming, billiards requires precision, strategy, and calculated moves. 
              The game teaches patience and the importance of thinking several shots ahead - 
              skills that translate well to algorithmic trading.
            </p>
            <div class="skills-tags">
              <span class="tag">Strategic Thinking</span>
              <span class="tag">Precision</span>
              <span class="tag">Focus</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Tennis Section -->
      <div class="gallery-section">
        <h2>üéæ Tennis</h2>
        <div class="activity-card">
          <div class="placeholder-image tennis">
            <span>üéæ</span>
            <p>Tennis Match</p>
          </div>
          <div class="activity-content">
            <h3>Quick Decisions Under Pressure</h3>
            <p>
              Tennis has taught me to make split-second decisions under pressure - 
              a skill invaluable in high-frequency trading where milliseconds matter. 
              The sport emphasizes adaptability and quick reflexes.
            </p>
            <div class="skills-tags">
              <span class="tag">Quick Reflexes</span>
              <span class="tag">Adaptability</span>
              <span class="tag">Endurance</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Snowboarding Section -->
      <div class="gallery-section">
        <h2>üèÇ Snowboarding</h2>
        <div class="activity-card">
          <div class="placeholder-image snowboarding">
            <span>üèÇ</span>
            <p>Mountain Adventure</p>
          </div>
          <div class="activity-content">
            <h3>Risk Assessment & Balance</h3>
            <p>
              Snowboarding combines risk assessment with the thrill of speed. 
              Each run requires evaluating terrain, conditions, and personal limits - 
              principles that apply directly to financial risk management.
            </p>
            <div class="skills-tags">
              <span class="tag">Risk Assessment</span>
              <span class="tag">Balance</span>
              <span class="tag">Adventure</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="gallery-stats">
      <h2>$ cat ~/sports_stats.json</h2>
      <div class="stats-container">
        <div class="stat-block">
          <pre><code>{`{
  "billiards": {
    "favorite_game": "8-ball",
    "best_run": "6 balls straight",
    "playing_since": "2018",
    "philosophy": "Every shot matters"
  },
  "tennis": {
    "playing_style": "Aggressive baseline",
    "favorite_surface": "Hard court", 
    "training_frequency": "2-3x per week",
    "motto": "Adapt and overcome"
  },
  "snowboarding": {
    "experience": "5+ years",
    "favorite_terrain": "All-mountain",
    "best_mountain": "To be conquered",
    "season_goal": "Master black diamonds"
  }
}`}</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="philosophy-section">
      <h2>## Life Balance Philosophy</h2>
      <blockquote>
        "The same principles that make you successful in sports - discipline, strategy, 
        continuous learning, and risk management - are the foundation of excellence in 
        technology and finance. Physical activities keep the mind sharp and provide 
        fresh perspectives for problem-solving."
      </blockquote>
      
      <div class="crossover-skills">
        <h3>Skills That Cross Over:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Precision:</strong> Billiards ‚Üí Code Quality ‚Üí Trading Execution</li>
          <li><strong>Quick Decision Making:</strong> Tennis ‚Üí System Response ‚Üí Market Timing</li>
          <li><strong>Risk Assessment:</strong> Snowboarding ‚Üí Portfolio Management ‚Üí System Architecture</li>
          <li><strong>Continuous Improvement:</strong> All Sports ‚Üí Learning New Technologies ‚Üí Strategy Optimization</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="upload-notice">
      <h3>üì∏ Photo Upload Coming Soon</h3>
      <p>
        This gallery currently shows placeholder content. Action shots and videos 
        from billiards tournaments, tennis matches, and snowboarding adventures 
        will be added soon to showcase these activities in action.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .gallery-page {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 1rem;
  }
  
  .gallery-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 3rem;
    margin: 3rem 0;
  }
  
  .gallery-section {
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }
  
  .gallery-section h2 {
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .activity-card {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.03);
  }
  
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .activity-card {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr;
    }
  }
  
  .placeholder-image {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    height: 200px;
    border: 2px dashed var(--accent);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.05);
    color: var(--accent);
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .placeholder-image span {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .placeholder-image p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
  
  .billiards {
    border-color: #10b981;
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.05);
    color: #10b981;
  }
  
  .tennis {
    border-color: #f59e0b;
    background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.05);
    color: #f59e0b;
  }
  
  .snowboarding {
    border-color: #3b82f6;
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.05);
    color: #3b82f6;
  }
  
  .activity-content h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  
  .skills-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
  
  .tag {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: var(--background);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  
  .gallery-stats {
    margin: 3rem 0;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
    background: rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.05);
  }
  
  .stats-container {
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }
  
  .stat-block {
    background: rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.1);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }
  
  .stat-block pre {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: 'Fira Code', monospace;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .philosophy-section {
    margin: 3rem 0;
    padding: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.03);
  }
  
  .philosophy-section h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  
  blockquote {
    border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .crossover-skills {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  
  .crossover-skills h3 {
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .crossover-skills ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  
  .crossover-skills li {
    margin: 1rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  
  .crossover-skills li::before {
    content: "‚Üí ";
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: bold;
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
  }
  
  .upload-notice {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border: 2px solid #6b7280;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: rgba(107, 114, 128, 0.05);
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .upload-notice h3 {
    color: #6b7280;
    margin-top: 0;
  }
  
  .upload-notice p {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
</style>